---
description: Kubebuilder marker policy for this repo. Apply when editing kubebuilder markers under api/v*/. XValidation is not supported.
globs: api/v*/**/*.go
alwaysApply: false
---

- XValidation (MUST NOT):
  - Do NOT use `+kubebuilder:validation:XValidation` in this repo.
  - Use standard validation markers instead (e.g., `Enum`, `MinLength`, `Minimum`).
